1 Fix: Some classes like EventListener does not have a self.window.. 2 Fix: Make a copy of the paths for use when retrying a command, like file exists, permission denied, etc [very old regression]

As self.window and view.window() is not that reliable in some circumstances we falling back to sublime.active_window() to get the current window. Turns out on Linux https://github.com/SideBarEnhancements-org/SideBarEnhancements/issues/351 and https://github.com/SublimeTextIssues/Core/issues/1520 this api appears to give the incorrect windows, so this commit try to use self.window and in any case fallback to sublime.active_window()
